                <text_1299650025
                        jcr:primaryType="cpp:Element"
                        sling:resourceType="composum/pages/components/element/text"
                        text="&lt;p>All functions of the various nodes tools (browser, user manager, package manager) can be restricted via declared rules. These rules are configured via OSGi and can thus be varied for different systems depending on the runmode. Individual features can be disabled (none), protected against modifications (read) or even explicitly and completely permitted (write) in deviation from the general setting via these explicit, functional service restrictions using the associated key.&lt;/p>">
